Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.50,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.11,0:00:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.58,0:00:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.49,0:00:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.16,0:00:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.91,0:01:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.39,0:01:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.02,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.13,0:01:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹得好\N活該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.61,0:02:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來難民就完全孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來只剩下在旁邊看著這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.28,0:02:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對孤獨毫無耐性之人們的困惑\N朝我想像的結局前進之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將會如何歸結而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.53,0:02:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#24  出島  空襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同伴被殺卻要求「不要開火」\N他們不會心服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.21,0:02:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰略情報部的報告指出\N剩下的核武全都在出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候應該不等武檢小組到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派遣機甲化部隊一口氣解決才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是有情報指出  我們要是派兵進入出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.42,0:02:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們很可能使用核武進行自殺炸彈攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要派兵的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.46,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先攻擊難民的武裝據點之後\N再派也不遲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要派上次那個無人駕駛攻擊直升機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.89,0:03:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.15,0:03:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛剛已經被解除內閣總理大臣的職務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理由呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你獨斷獨行邀請聯合國武檢小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在緊急狀態法制下  有可能被視為叛國罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此在這件事告一段落之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉我們必須逮捕您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰的權限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公安9課荒卷課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.95,0:03:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您也有教唆叛國罪的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請乖乖回房間去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  你們這些人到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從6小時前開始  就聯絡不上荒卷課長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還在官邸的地下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那聯絡上之後幫我轉告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.52,0:04:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想這恐怕是內廳的情報操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.02,0:04:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  難民威脅將用核武\N做自殺攻擊的傳聞甚囂塵上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該有什麼內幕請他調查看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依你的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.94,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該已經掌握到什麼線索才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那個時候一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.86,0:05:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府一開始就打算這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.26,0:05:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自衛軍那些混蛋敢進來出島試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把武器放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上收起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都不要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要收起武器  他們就不會打過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.74,0:05:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是久世？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是…久世同志？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點就打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找幾個高手到這裏集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.20,0:06:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓大家再次跟我的電子腦連線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.54,0:06:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.38,0:06:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟以前在新濱難民居住區\N進行的聯合演習一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.25,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入出島的話\N恐怕連軍方的識別密碼都會失效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.69,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,細腰蜂會無條件攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟自己不同形狀的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.43,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波瑪  動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  波瑪  跟我交換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊已經開始了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  好像沒有我們上場的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.75,0:07:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要核武還沒回收就不可能登陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那跟我們無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸自特種部隊打算秘密進入出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回收核彈的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校  快要進入通信障礙區域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算通信斷絕還是要把回路打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有必須掌握海上的動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前細腰蜂正在等間隔盤旋中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好低空接近\N例如轉進那棟高大建築物的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斷線了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:07:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從出島北側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.51,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有架識別密碼錯誤的直升機接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在ECM區域內消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,electronic countermeasure 電子干擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該就是那個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用同樣的航線進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.92,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通訊終於斷絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生沒事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些黑心肝的AI真的很兇惡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯  確實如此\N好擔心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊  是啊\N有點恐怖耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.34,0:08:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來  那傢伙跟石川先生會合了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  跟石川先生會合了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能那麼快到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.58,0:08:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是在地面上做物理移動喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼石川先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也正在趕過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.29,0:09:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能太著急結果被抓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一直用影像確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.11,0:09:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是上次那個細腰蜂掌握制空權\N我覺得很危險…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又無法跟課長取得聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.78,0:09:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來從這時候開始\N只能靠自己的判斷行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.19,0:09:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民與久世  政府與合田\N課長和少校  還有我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.20,0:09:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠做出最優秀單獨演出的人\N好像就能左右這個事件的勝敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛4課的直升機進入出島了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.08,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此一來  鈽的回收就有辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.78,0:10:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鈽的回收並不是我\N派出4課的真正理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您的意思是…
